qevercloud
------------------------------------------
This library presents the complete Evernote SDK for Qt. All the functionality
that is described on Evernote site is implemented and ready to use. In
particular OAuth authentication is implemented.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libQt5Core5-5.9.4-2
  libQt5Gui5-5.9.4-2
  libQt5WebKit5-5.9.3-0.3.20180115git
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libqt5qevercloud6-6.1.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libQt5Gui-devel-5.9.4-2
  libQt5WebKit-devel-5.9.3-0.3.20180115git
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/d1vanov/QEverCloud

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/d1vanov/QEverCloud/archive/refs/tags/v6.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack qevercloud-6.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./qevercloud-6.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/qevercloud-6.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/qevercloud-6.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqt5qevercloud6-6.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqt5qevercloud-devel-6.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

